            <title>[THRIFT-2957] warning: source file %s is in a subdirectory, but option &apos;subdir-objects&apos; is disabled</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-2957</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;automake&lt;/tt&gt; produces a lot of these errors and in the &lt;tt&gt;configure.ac&lt;/tt&gt; file the line with &lt;tt&gt;AM_INIT_AUTOMAKE(&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;...&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/tt&gt; does not contain &lt;tt&gt;subdir-objects&lt;/tt&gt; as an option.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Ubuntu on EC2 and OS X on a Macbook Pro,&lt;br/&gt;
openSUSE&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
